title: Little Big Town Performs TV Show Theme Songs + Raymundo Reveals His Groomsman Count + Lunchbox Gets Mad At An Airplane Passenger
itunes:title: Little Big Town Performs TV Show Theme Songs + Raymundo Reveals His Groomsman Count + Lunchbox Gets Mad At An Airplane Passenger
description:
Little Big Town stops by the studio to talk about their new music, pick which of their hit songs they would stop playing at their concerts and to perform TV theme songs. Raymundo gives us a wedding update about his groomsmen count and whether some of the guys from the show will be included. Lunchbox got mad a guy on a SW flight who wouldn’t let him save a seat for his wife.
